headline: PARAMOUNT APPOINTS MAKAN DELRAHIM AS CHIEF LEGAL OFFICER
summary: Paramount Skydance Corporation (Nasdaq: PSKY) today announced the appointment of Makan Delrahim as Chief Legal Officer, effective October 6, 2025. In this role, Delrahim will oversee all legal, regulatory, compliance and public policy matters for the Company, including oversight of Paramount's Government Relations team.

headline: Is Paramount Skydance Stock Outperforming the S&P 500?
